node.text:
For me, hockey is more than just a sport. It’s a lifestyle. 
From endless hours on the pond to 3am chel sessions, there are so many ways to play the game that we love. I’m pumped to announce that I’ll be joining the @BauerHockey team as an Official Bauer Athlete in growing our beautiful game together. This is just the beginning.

node.text: EA SPORTS NHL 20 officially launches worldwide September 13 with Auston Matthews as the global cover athlete. In NHL 20, your favorite NHL stars now look and feel more authentic with new Signature Shots and over 45 new shot types that make every attack a threat. A new broadcast package celebrates your biggest plays as you take on all-new game modes, including the new winner-take-all Eliminator mode where you play solo or team up with friends to take down the competition. #NHL20 #EAAmbassador

node.text:
Pumped to announce I’ll be co-hosting the @bluejacketsnhl pre-draft show! 

Friday night at Nationwide Arena, the entire broadcast crew and myself will be live on the big stage talking with players, coaches, & more. Come out to the free DRAFT PARTY to meet me, have some fun, and see who we take at #5 in the draft. LET’S GO. #CBJ

node.text:
Rest In Peace, Kivi💔

Last week, I had the chance to meet & play roller hockey with Kivi….today, he passed away in a tragic accident. Such a great guy with a pure heart on & off the ice. Please keep his his family, friends, and teammates in your prayers🙏🏼
